701516f-a.title: Bronx: River Avenue - 164th Street (East)
701516f-a.text:
Mullaly Park: A view eastward across the section of the park
which is located between East 165th (left) and East 164th Streeta. Also
shown is the elevated structure of the Woodlawn subway line on River Ave.
The vantage-point is the Park Plaza Building on the west side of Jerome
Ave.
1936.
Works Progress Administration.
Federal Writers' Project photo.
CREDIT LINE IMPERATIVE ON ALL REPRODUCTIONS.
